# Building the mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin Site

To build and view the rendered site, run these commands **from the `mkdocs-live-wysiwyg-plugin` directory**:

```bash
../techdocs-preview.sh add_plugins --upgrade .
../techdocs-preview.sh build
```

Use this workflow any time you wish to view the rendered site. Do **not** use `mkdocs build` or `mkdocs serve` directly; use the techdocs-preview script instead.
